OL,3,CAlcohol price increase described as
OL,4,C'really disappointing'
OL,6,FAn increase in the price of alcohol in
OL,7,FWales has been described by Welsh
OL,8,FConservative critics as "really
OL,9,Fdisappointing".
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV Wales' Sharp End,
OL,12,FWelsh Conservative candidate Calum
OL,13,FDavies said the policy does not work.
OL,15,FHe said: "I used to work in health
OL,16,Fpolicy and I remember looking at the
OL,17,Fevidence for when it came out of
OL,18,FScotland, where they'd also done it,
OL,19,Fand guess what: It does not work."
