OL,6,FOn Tuesday (4 February), the Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment announced that Senedd
OL,8,Fmembers had approved a proposal to
OL,9,Fincrease the minimum unit price (MUP)
OL,10,Ffrom 50p to 65p.
OL,12,FMr Davies said: "It's really
OL,13,Fdisappointing to see the Senedd of
OL,14,Fgive this re-endorsement and an
OL,15,Fincrease to the MUP."
OL,17,FThe Welsh Government argued the policy
OL,18,Fwill "save lives and help protect many
OL,19,Fpeople from the harms caused by
OL,20,Fdrinking too much alcohol".
