OL,6,FShavanah Taj, who is a Labour
OL,7,Fcandidate in May's Senedd election,
OL,8,Fadded: "This is about reducing harm
OL,9,Ffor people, and the number of people
OL,10,Fwho are hazardous drinkers."
OL,12,FPlaid Cymru's Luke Fletcher MS argued:
OL,13,F"You can also point to evidence that
OL,14,Fshows that alcohol-related deaths have
OL,15,Fdropped by 29% in Scotland.
OL,17,F"There is a public health message here
OL,18,Fthat we need to remember.
